summary: All three requirements (REQ-91, REQ-92, REQ-93) have been successfully implemented. The logo has been repositioned in both Navigation.tsx and Home.tsx with proper spacing, alignment, and responsive sizing. The logo path references /assets/generated/logo.dim_512x512.png in both files.

hallucinated_features.description: Logo file path changed to /assets/generated/logo.dim_512x512.png instead of /assets/logo.png
hallucinated_features.reason: REQ-93 specifies the logo should be at frontend/public/assets/logo.png (or frontend/public/assets/generated/logo.png if generated) and referenced using absolute paths starting with /assets/. The implementation uses /assets/generated/logo.dim_512x512.png with specific dimensions suffix (_512x512), which was not mentioned in the requirements.
